title: Syllabus mentioned in ERP
text: Soil stabilization, resilient modulus, and fatigue of bituminous mixtures, design of emulsified mixes, Benkelman Beam tests, Roughness survey of roads, Pavement evaluation using DCP, Falling Weight Deflectometer, Axle Load Survey, Traffic data collection and analysis.
